type: TS LF Trading Bot Error - Execution Unexpected Error

definition.text: An Unexpected Error occured while procesing the execution of orders. The LF Trading Bot continued running after reporting this error.

paragraphs.text: The error prevented the LF Trading Bot from performing certain operations.
In the following section you will find the specific information received when this error occured.
